author: Bill Mahoney
title: Rhode Island ends restrictions on New Yorkers
description: Cuomo said he had spoken with Raimondo on Saturday and that she told him her executive order was being repealed.
content:
Rhode Island Gov. Gina Raimondo | AP Photo
Rhode Island Gov. Gina Raimondo has backed down from restricting New Yorkers' access to her state, Gov. Andrew Cuomo said Sunday afternoon.
